{"tid":1814841,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"人人都可以係勇武","createTime":"2020-01-07T05:54:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T06:04:05.000Z","uid":208086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ea5d6bd09d2a78a0bd92f9290155c07487d0a637","tid":1814841,"uid":208086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T05:54:43.000Z","msg":"唔捉鬼已經係共識，(真)勇武退場亦一定有原因，但一開始無勇武，點解之後有，因為佢哋有不畏強權既心同一往無前既勇氣。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E48ozpk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE48ozpk.gif&h=73f663d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n引用周星馳喺食神既一段台詞，勇武唔係一班人，而係一種精神，個個都可以係勇武，只要有不畏強權既心同一往無前既勇氣。<br />\n<br />\n依家已經和勇不分，保持獨立思考，分清分化風向，推返行程表<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wcRESeq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwcRESeq.jpg&h=3a57025d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d113fa9a6b6c0815b82b9a9af46e28095cc3b1b3","tid":1814841,"uid":208086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T05:55:22.000Z","msg":"分和勇"},{"pid":"a8a91bf0c0bfc172589d66d07022ecb1d12ebcbe","tid":1814841,"uid":208086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T05:56:28.000Z","msg":"十連推 1"},{"pid":"0b77cbc376e24daee33426c70f28f6fd59b0eba6","tid":1814841,"uid":120955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T05:56:46.000Z","msg":"和理非可以勇武<br />\n勇武都可以和理非<br />\n遊行日子咪同和理非一齊行，要啲鬼都一齊行囉"},{"pid":"c9af52ad69c6b053caed762fedff699e84f83d6a","tid":1814841,"uid":208086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T05:57:48.000Z","msg":"和勇分2"},{"pid":"6a60a65882d06093a01d144b11bfccf701b35a96","tid":1814841,"uid":208086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T05:58:11.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"8accfd43d41013d197dd1e94d03fc4a4aa69d042","tid":1814841,"uid":208086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T05:58:47.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"055eece9a46d35974f169ec2352a1d975024878c","tid":1814841,"uid":208086,"like"